**Yodel.\
\
   Attached you\'ll find the 2 books, \"All aboard the birthday boat\",
and, \"Pancakes for everyone.\" We\'re really looking to make these
books timeless. Angela has poured her heart into these and more to
follow. \
\
   As you may know - children\'s books have 2 markets - children and
their parents. The art needs to be captivating enough for both parents
and kids to be like, \"Whats that?\" when looking at a boookshelf.
Additionally, the book needs to read well enough to where a parent
doesn\'t mind reading it to their child - whether it be the literal
content, or the delivery of that content. We really believe the text
content is quality in terms of what it\'s saying as well as how it\'s
saying it - it\'s fun to read. We really want you to explore your
mind\'s eye when reading these. **

**   We really do believe this could be all of our big break. I have a
few connections and a line-drive pathway to publishing and distribution.
With Angelas credentials and writing, your outstanding artwork, and my
ability to market and deliver the books to consumers, we may have a
home-run. I hope you see it that way, too. \
\
These first few may look great with watercolor as you had previously
mentioned. Some books moving forward we even may want to do comic-style,
we\'ll keep you in the loop - and we\'ll likely want your input on a lot
of this, too. We would like to consider you a partner in this series of
books. \
\
Please reach out if you have any questions, comments, concerns along the
way. \
\
Best!\
Beanie man**
